        <div class="description">
          <p>
            ✨ <strong>CodeRank</strong> by <strong>RID Tech</strong> is a
            next-generation learning platform built exclusively for students and
            aspiring developers. RID Tech works towards bridging the gap between
            academic learning and real-world industry requirements by providing
            structured programming practice, smart solutions, and an interactive
            code runner. Our mission is to empower every student with practical
            coding skills and confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="features-section">
          <h2>🚀 What's New</h2>
          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="goToCodeRunner()">
              <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
              <h3>Code Runner</h3>
              <p>
                Execute code instantly in the browser – see output or errors in
                real time.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="godsa()">
              <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
              <h3>DSA & Interview Prep</h3>
              <p>
                Build strong problem-solving skills, master data structures and
                algorithms, and prepare for coding interviews.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="aihint()">
              <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
              <h3>AI Hints</h3>
              <p>
                Stuck on a problem? Get AI-powered step-by-step hints without
                spoiling the solution.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="progress()">
              <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
              <h3>Progress Analytics</h3>
              <p>
                Analyze your performance, monitor solved problems, and identify
                areas for improvement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
